<canvas height="600" >
   <!-- fonts both included and client fonts -->
    <font src="fonts/FuturNo2DBol_small.ttf" name="futura" />
	
	<simplelayout spacing="20" />
	<view layout="spacing:5" >
		<text> For the examples below, there is no height adjustment for the font sizes 12,14,16 </text>
	
		<text text="Welcome you! gpq" bgcolor="0x00FF00" 
			  resize="true" fgcolor="0x52529B" font="futura" fontsize="12" />
			  
		<text text="Welcome you! gpq" bgcolor="0x00FF00" 
			  resize="true" fgcolor="0x52529B" font="futura" fontsize="14" />
			  
		<text text="Welcome you! gpq" bgcolor="0x00FF00" 
			  resize="true" fgcolor="0x52529B" font="futura" fontsize="16" />
	</view>

	<view layout="spacing:5">
		<text> For the examples below ( fontsize 12,14,16 ), the height is adjusted with a constraint </text>
		<text> constraint: height="${1.4*this.getTextHeight()}" </text>
		<text text="Welcome you! gpq" bgcolor="0x00FF00" 
			  resize="true" fgcolor="0x52529B" font="futura" fontsize="12" 
			  height="${1.4*this.getTextHeight()}" />
	
		<text text="Welcome you! gpq" bgcolor="0x00FF00" 
			  resize="true" fgcolor="0x52529B" font="futura" fontsize="14" 
			  height="${1.4*this.getTextHeight()}" />
	 
		<text text="Welcome you! gpq" bgcolor="0x00FF00" 
			  resize="true" fgcolor="0x52529B" font="futura" fontsize="16" 
			  height="${1.4*this.getTextHeight()}" />
	</view>

	<view layout="spacing:5">
		<text> For the examples below ( fontsize 12,14,16 ), the height is adjusted with a constraint </text>
		<text> constraint: height="${this.getTextHeight() + 4}" </text>
		<text text="Welcome you! gpq" bgcolor="0x00FF00" 
			  resize="true" fgcolor="0x52529B" font="futura" fontsize="12" 
			  height="${this.getTextHeight() + 4}" />
	
		<text text="Welcome you! gpq" bgcolor="0x00FF00" 
			  resize="true" fgcolor="0x52529B" font="futura" fontsize="14" 
			  height="${this.getTextHeight() + 4}" />
	 
		<text text="Welcome you! gpq" bgcolor="0x00FF00" 
			  resize="true" fgcolor="0x52529B" font="futura" fontsize="16" 
			  height="${this.getTextHeight() + 4}" />
	</view>

</canvas>